we are going to use omdb api
https://www.omdbapi.com/

currenttoff

My OMDb API: http://www.omdbapi.com/?i=tt3896198&apikey=a2ce51a6

how to use OMdb API
Send all data requests to:

http://www.omdbapi.com/?apikey=[yourkey]&

Poster API requests:

http://img.omdbapi.com/?apikey=[yourkey]&

